{"tid":1500890,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"GTA FiveM RP Server 香城RP 招人","createTime":"2019-08-24T07:27:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T00:40:11.000Z","uid":136737,"like":12,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6e9cfde20e227b7e4b08e4a2a4dc47c4344cc420","tid":1500890,"uid":136737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T07:27:41.000Z","msg":"伺服器背景：<br />\n其實呢個server公測咗一排 收集唔同玩家的意見和建議 改善伺服器的質素 而家完咗公測 所以改咗伺服器名 重新開post.<br />\n<br />\n伺服器特色：<br />\n<br />\n1) 玩家可以自創自己嘅職業 提交簡單嘅劇本 admin睇完覺得有RP的可能性同空間 就會係維護時幫大家加落去 <br />\n例子：<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/602567966944526337/611475390824841216/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F602567966944526337%2F611475390824841216%2Funknown.png&h=99efff63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/602567966944526337/611474837940207635/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F602567966944526337%2F611474837940207635%2Funknown.png&h=b36afc63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2)為咗確保伺服器公平性 <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">本伺服器不提供課金服務</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n3) 鼓勵玩家自己搞活動俾大家參與 admin得閒亦會以普通玩家的身份參與其中 唔會小圈子 <br />\n例子：<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/607929824291454989/611192411896676356/20190726175229_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F607929824291454989%2F611192411896676356%2F20190726175229_1.jpg&h=99a2c71f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/607929824291454989/611192319173197824/20190728223306_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F607929824291454989%2F611192319173197824%2F20190728223306_1.jpg&h=6aa7763e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/602567966944526337/611247751451377701/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F602567966944526337%2F611247751451377701%2Funknown.png&h=79be363e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4) 玩家亦可以係Discord頻道同admin申請唔同活動同宣傳 如果用呢個方法申請的話 亦可要求admin幫手籌備活動<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/611481377698742282/611483044452499470/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F611481377698742282%2F611483044452499470%2Funknown.png&h=b6551a0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/611481377698742282/611483725913653250/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F611481377698742282%2F611483725913653250%2Funknown.png&h=43281803&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5) 設有新聞頻道 畀冇入game嘅玩家大約知道入面發生乜事<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/611481377698742282/611484921344557076/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F611481377698742282%2F611484921344557076%2Funknown.png&h=2788b2f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/611481377698742282/611485277600612371/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F611481377698742282%2F611485277600612371%2Funknown.png&h=59a1e0b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6) 各種唔同嘅地點畀各位玩家發揮 例如：教堂，婚禮場地，記協等等<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/611481377698742282/611486354424987658/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F611481377698742282%2F611486354424987658%2Funknown.png&h=1ac69d94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/611481377698742282/611487534601601024/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F611481377698742282%2F611487534601601024%2Funknown.png&h=220e4950&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/611481377698742282/611487901632692234/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F611481377698742282%2F611487901632692234%2Funknown.png&h=bba99c72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7)多元化嘅模組 例子：需要互動嘅打劫系統，可以in game通話嘅電話，玩家可自己購買便利店出售物品，餐廳，夜店等<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/611481377698742282/611489433790840832/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F611481377698742282%2F611489433790840832%2Funknown.png&h=0ea08b10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/611481377698742282/611489601080786954/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F611481377698742282%2F611489601080786954%2Funknown.png&h=02ea7a4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/611481377698742282/611489804986744832/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F611481377698742282%2F611489804986744832%2Funknown.png&h=bfab7bf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/611481377698742282/611490013409968138/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F611481377698742282%2F611490013409968138%2Funknown.png&h=280c6fa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/611481377698742282/611490135955210260/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F611481377698742282%2F611490135955210260%2Funknown.png&h=a7c0f48c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/611481377698742282/611490655440601088/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F611481377698742282%2F611490655440601088%2Funknown.png&h=37800696&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/611481377698742282/611491023666937856/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F611481377698742282%2F611491023666937856%2Funknown.png&h=2425c6e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8) 有admin log 記錄admin工作 而且admin係現實都唔係個個都互相認識 可以避免出現小圈子同濫權問題 而且我地會盡量安排最少1個admin上線 解決玩家的問題<br />\n<br />\n9) 特別加入本港特色車輛 增加玩家代入感<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/611481377698742282/611492538007814144/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F611481377698742282%2F611492538007814144%2Funknown.png&h=9355f324&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n10) 加入大量現實模組車供玩家選擇 而且每架都以現實性能作參考 經過平衡 唔會出現所謂嘅外掛車<br />\n<br />\n活動預告：30/8/2019 10pm 第一屆紐伯林大賽車 歡迎大家加入參與 <br />\n場地預覽圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/596329889884536846/614717463153868811/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F596329889884536846%2F614717463153868811%2Funknown.png&h=cf5d37ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/596329889884536846/614717725528555541/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F596329889884536846%2F614717725528555541%2Funknown.png&h=95541d26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加入方法：<br />\n1) 加入香城RP Discord (Link: <a href=\"https://discord.gg/Ff8GJbH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FFf8GJbH&d=LRWPp57H9HH2b7ruXTkGLlgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=b9173a5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/Ff8GJbH</a> )<br />\n2) 根據Welcomer所發出的表格 填寫簡單資料申請白名單 (表格需遞交到discord內的入境申請區)<br />\n3) 等待admin或資深玩家聯絡 (會循例問下有冇經驗 簡單講下我地伺服器的規則等等) 其間其他admin會幫手加白名單<br />\n4) 進入伺服器設計角色後，需要調節GTA 5語音聊天同設定電話<br />\n5) 完成 可以享受遊戲 冇經驗的玩家有機會獲得其他資深玩家的新手嚮導 非強制性 可以拒絕<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DGhdANu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDGhdANu.png&h=fd03876c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"058deb14ed0f60702a0785cc367a87b3a00196cf","tid":1500890,"uid":206671,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T07:31:02.000Z","msg":"我鍾意打機但不過有時間就出街發夢仲好"},{"pid":"4fa3948dc245a238d6f0d6d6c0039cc1a7ce3570","tid":1500890,"uid":136737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:15:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"93ee73f86f7bfd04babfadb67a813b90d6ce6c67","tid":1500890,"uid":136737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T09:05:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"04a9734f495217cac0c87a6094bd845ddc847b66","tid":1500890,"uid":136737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T10:18:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"253268ab173898c69ba4282906cb13694279ded4","tid":1500890,"uid":45613,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"058deb14ed0f60702a0785cc367a87b3a00196cf","tid":1500890,"uid":206671,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T07:31:02.000Z","msg":"我鍾意打機但不過有時間就出街發夢仲好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T10:20:53.000Z","msg":"Both la <br />\nNeed balance"},{"pid":"3beff132e55f7646d7331980b1736372edc6de8a","tid":1500890,"uid":210165,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:34:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fccbf3f212ffaa20462e82bf0cf894ba7885e309","tid":1500890,"uid":6142,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3beff132e55f7646d7331980b1736372edc6de8a","tid":1500890,"uid":210165,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:34:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:25:48.000Z","msg":"發完夢翻去打<br />\n利申 發完夢"},{"pid":"fcb2e14a595483ee2dd